details.biography: Peggy Lu is an American actress, who is best known for Venom: Let There Be Carnage (2021), Venom (2018), and Kung Pow: Enter the Fist (2002). Born on February 22, 1963, Peggy hails from New York, United States.
details.name: Peggy Lu
details.place_of_birth: New York City, New York, USA
